item.title: Real teleports with levels [delta]
item.dc:creator: @ravens ravens
item.description:
@ravens wrote:

it would be in clickingmost.java, i believe case 4140? anyways just tele home on your server, do ::mypos, and search the first number in clickingmost.java.
it will be like:

case 4140:
c.triggertele(####, ####);
break;

you have to make it like:

case 4140:// #### = item id, 1 = item amount
if ((c.getinventory.hasitem(####, 1) && (c.getinventory.hasitem(####, 1) && (c.getinventory.hasitem(####, 1)){
c.triggertele(####, ####);
c.deleteitem(####, 1);
c.deleteitem(####, 1);
c.deleteitem(####, 1);
} else {
c.sM("You do not have the required runes to cast this spell.");
}
break;
